data.description: Welcome!  This all-brick, 1965 construction home will check off all of your wish-list items!  Located in the sought-after Parkview cluster, Brady Drive is super close to shopping, schools, churches, restaurants, Stone Mountain Park, downtown Lilburn and downtown Tucker!  A few additional details about this property:  original hardwood floors, new interior and exterior paint, separate den, formal living room, formal dining room, bonus room / added den with huge brick fireplace - perfect for rec room / home office / in-law suite, large patio overlooking private and fenced backyard with storage shed. newer HVAC and water heater, new gutters, large corner lot with only hardwood trees, a cozy front porch, updated lighting...Just adorable!  Come see - stay a while!
